<tr><td colspan=3D\"1\"><span style=3D\"color: rgb(123, 57, 0);\">&laquo;He=
rmanos que se aman a pesar de sus diferencias&raquo;: esta definici&oac=
ute;n de la Iglesia que el papa ha dado hace poco ante los obispos amig=
os del movimiento de los focolares (<a href=3D\"http://www.pl002.net/aff=
_lettre.asp?LET_N_ID=3D2177\">ver el correo</a> en franc&eacute;s n&ordm=
; 431), evidentemente, no ha llegado a&uacute;n a o&iacute;dos de los o=
bispos de Costa Rica. En la archidi&oacute;cesis de San Jos&eacute;, el=
 trato reservado a la joven asociaci&oacute;n <span style=3D\"font-style=
: italic;\">Una Voce</span> no s&oacute;lo est&aacute; desprovisto de to=
da caridad, sino hasta del m&aacute;s simple sentido com&uacute;n. Sin =
embargo, este asunto prueba, por el absurdo, la universalidad de la mis=
a tradicional.</span><br/><br/><div><img src=3D\"http://www.bhgfd.com/se=
curefilesystem/images/rs20150204154955_misaCostaRica.jpg\" style=3D\"widt=
h: 600px;\"></div><span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">Una de las misas d=
e </span>Una Voce<span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\"> Costa Rica. Celeb=
rada un s&aacute;bado, a puertas cerradas, atrajo demasiada gente para =
el arzobispado, que ha justificado as&iacute; su negativa a aplicar el =
</span>motu proprio<span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\"> de Benedicto XV=
I.</span><br/><br/><br/><div><span style=3D\"font-weight: bold;\">I &ndas=
h; EL COMUNICADO OFICIAL DE <span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">UNA VOC=
E</span> COSTA RICA</span></div><div><br/>Invitamos a nuestros lectores=
 <a href=3D\"http://www.unavocecr.com/2014/03/comunicado-oficial-misa-tr=
identina.html\">a leer aqu&iacute;</a> con provecho, si a&uacute;n no lo=
 conocen, el largo, preciso y valiente comunicado emitido el 14 de marz=
o de 2014 por la filial costarricense de <span style=3D\"font-style: ita=
lic;\">Una Voce</span>.<br/><br/><div>En su momento, no lo comentamos, c=
on la esperanza de que la publicidad dada al asunto incitara a las auto=
ridades eclesi&aacute;sticas locales a rever su postura. Por desgracia,=
 los corazones de algunos pastores son, realmente, de piedra, y el 7 de=
 julio de 2014, UV Costa Rica publicaba en su sitio Internet<a href=3D\"=
http://www.unavocecr.com/2014/07/summorum-pontificum-fiasco-en-costa-ri=
ca.html\"> un nuevo texto</a>, suerte de r&eacute;quiem por la aplicaci&=
oacute;n del motu proprio <span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">Summorum =
Pontificum</span> en dicho pa&iacute;s.<br/><br/>Este asunto, que contr=
adice el hecho, expresado por el papa Francisco desde las primeras sema=
nas de su pontificado, de que no era cuesti&oacute;n de volver atr&aacu=
te;s con el texto de Benedicto XVI y reabrir la guerra lit&uacute;rgica=
 (<a href=3D\"http://es.pl002.net/aff_lettre.asp?LET_N_ID=3D2032\">ver nu=
estro correo 36</a>), nos inspira los comentarios del mes.<br/><br/><br=
/><span style=3D\"font-weight: bold;\">II &ndash; LAS REFLEXIONES DE <spa=
n style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">PAIX LITURGIQUE</span></span><br/><br/>=
1) En su &uacute;ltima asamblea general de 2013, la Federaci&oacute;n I=
nternacional <span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">Una Voce</span> (FIUV)=
 anunci&oacute; que 17 nuevos miembros se hab&iacute;an adherido desde =
el motu proprio de 2007. Ocho de estos diecisiete miembros provienen de=
 Hispanoam&eacute;rica y lo que los caracteriza es que est&aacute;n rep=
resentados por j&oacute;venes. La liturgia tradicional es, pues, un tes=
oro para toda la Iglesia (<a href=3D\"http://es.pl002.net/texte.asp?TEX_=
N_ID=3D796\">Instrucci&oacute;n Univers&aelig; Ecclesi&aelig;</a>) y atr=
ae de modo especial a los j&oacute;venes que jam&aacute;s la hab&iacute=
;an conocido (<a href=3D\"http://es.pl002.net/texte.asp?TEX_N_ID=3D99\">c=
arta de Benedicto XVI a los obispos</a>).<br/><br/>2) Es dif&iacute;cil=
 saber qu&eacute; ha pasado por la mente de Mons. Barrantes quien, en u=
n primer momento, hab&iacute;a permitido los preparativos para la celeb=
raci&oacute;n de la misa tradicional a los fieles que se lo hab&iacute;=
an pedido, y, en un segundo tiempo, les ha cerrado la puerta. Ahora bie=
n, la experiencia demuestra que los sacerdotes suelen aprovechar el hec=
ho de &laquo;estar reci&eacute;n nombrados&raquo; o de &laquo;tener que=
 dejar pronto la parroquia&raquo; para congelar toda aplicaci&oacute;n =
del motu proprio <span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">Summorum Pontificu=
m</span>. Mons. Barrantes, que estaba pr&oacute;ximo a retirarse, &ique=
st;simplemente hizo lo mismo, prefiriendo pasar &laquo;la patata calien=
te&raquo; a su sucesor? Sea como fuere, <span style=3D\"font-weight: bol=
d;\">no dejamos de asombrarnos ante la actitud de estos obispos que logr=
an conciliar interminables discursos sobre la apertura y el di&aacute;l=
ogo con el mayor desprecio hacia los fieles que no encajan con su visi&=
oacute;n de la Iglesia</span>.<br/><br/>3) La confrontaci&oacute;n con =
la dura realidad de la jerarqu&iacute;a eclesi&aacute;stica, incluida l=
a impotencia de la comisi&oacute;n <span style=3D\"font-style: italic;\">=
Ecclesia Dei</span>, no parece hacer mella en la energ&iacute;a reconfo=
rtante que manifiesta el comunicado de <span style=3D\"font-style: itali=
c;\">Una Voce</span> Costa Rica. <span style=3D\"font-weight: bold;\">Cabe=
 destacar que el eco hallado &laquo;en las bases&raquo; tanto entre los=
 sacerdotes como entre los fieles interesados por la misa tradicional e=
s una recompensa a la asociaci&oacute;n por sus esfuerzos.</span> Aun c=
uando los fieles est&aacute;n privados de misa p&uacute;blica, sabemos =
que pueden asistir a ella en privado y, adem&aacute;s, acudir al aposto=
lado de la FSSPX.<br/><br/>4) &laquo;En nuestro pa&iacute;s existe una =
prohibici&oacute;n silenciosa de facto contra la Misa que vivieron todo=
s los santos, desde San Gregorio Magno a San Francisco de As&iacute;s y=
 al Cura de Ars, culminando con el padre P&iacute;o&raquo;. Humanamente=
, es normal que despu&eacute;s de tantos a&ntilde;os de prohibici&oacut=
e;n abusiva de la misa tradicional, aunque nunca haya sido abrogada (&l=
aquo;numquam abrogatam&raquo;, art&iacute;culo 1&ordm; de <span style=3D=
\"font-style: italic;\"><a href=3D\"http://es.pl002.net/texte.asp?TEX_N_ID=
=3D96\" target=3D\"_blank\">Summorum Pontificum</a></span>), subsistan aqu=
&iacute; y all&aacute; resistencias a la rehabilitaci&oacute;n de la li=
turgia latina gregoriana. No obstante, <span style=3D\"font-weight: bold=
;\">nuestros amigos de Costa Rica no deben perder la confianza, porque a=
un cuando este tesoro de la Iglesia puede ser puesto bajo el celem&iacu=
te;n, de ninguna manera puede ser destruido. Es lo que nos ense&ntilde;=
a la historia y lo que tratamos de mostrar en nuestros correos.</span><=
/div></div><div><span style=3D\"font-weight: bold;\"><br/></span></div><d=
iv><span style=3D\"font-weight: bold;\"><img src=3D\"http://www.bhgfd.com/=

\"You, Sir, are having a stroke.\" 




That's what the ER doctor told me. 


I had come to see him because my eyes were pounding, my
vision was blurry, and I was blacking out multiple times a day. 

As it turns out, it was all because of my high blood pressure,
which was a deadly 201/100. 

He said if I didn't lower my blood pressure fast, I was a dead
man.  
So he put me on 6 different meds. 
 Unfortunately, none of them worked, and the side-effects
were horrendous. 
Then I heard from a man in Texas named Ken who had
discovered a way to lower blood pressure naturally, using
nothing but food. 
Ken said anybody suffering from high blood pressure should
drop whatever they're doing, drive to the nearest grocery
store, and buy this one food: 


1 food that kills high blood pressure


Nothing else was working, so I took Ken's advice.  

 You will not believe what happened next (click on the link
above to learn the rest).  

God Bless,  

Dan 



P.S. I know it sounds too easy. I thought so too. But read the rest of the story before you make up your mind. I think you'll
be glad you did... and it just might save your life.

porter in  hasty



terror performed his office, throwing open the  great door,   the populace would have saved him the trouble. The  instant he
had doneso, the affrighted janitor fled,  like one who



has drawn the bolts of a flood-gate, and expects to be overwhelmed by the rushing inundation. The monks, with 63H1I348DN one consent, had withdrawn
themselves behind  the Abbot, who


alone kept his station, about three yards from the entrance, showing  no  63H1I348DN signs of fear or perturbation. His brethren  partly
encouraged by his devotion,  partly ashamed to


desert him, and partly animated by a sense of duty. remained huddled close together, at  the back of their  Superior. There was a loud
laugh and huzza when the doors were opened;


but, contrary to what might have been expected, no crowd of enraged hiailants rushed into the church. On the contrary, there was a cry of A halt!-a
halt  63H1I348DN to order, my


masters! and let the two reverend fathers greet each other, as beseems them.  The appearance of the crowd who  were  thus called  to
order,


was grotesque in the extreme. It was composed of men, women, and children,  ludicrously disguised 63H1I348DN in various habits, and presenting
groups equally diversified and grotesque.

was supposed to hide the body of the animal,



ambled, caracoled, pranced, and plunged, as he performed the celebrated part of the hobby-horse,16 so often alluded to in our ancient drama; and which
still flourishes on 63H1I348DN



the stage  in the battle that concludes Bayess tragedy. To rival the address and 63H1I348DN agility displayed by this character, another 
personage advanced in the  more formidable


character 63H1I348DN of a huge dragon, with  gilded wings, open jaws, and a scarlet tongue, cloven at the end, which made various efforts to
overtake and devour a  lad, dressed as the



lovely Sabaea, daughter of the King of Egypt, who  fled before him; while a martial Saint George, grotesquely armed with a goblet for a helmet,
and a spit for a lance, ever and



anon interfered, and compelled the monster to relinquish his prey. A bear,  a wolf, and one or two other wild animals, played their parts with
the discretion of Snug the  joiner;



for the decided preference which they gave to the use of their hind legs,  was sufficient, without any formal annunciation, to hiure the most
timorous spectators that



they had to do with habitual bipeds. There was a group of outlaws with Robin Hood and Little John at their head17  the best representation exhibited
at   the time; and no


great wonder, since most of the actors were, by profession, the banished   men and thieves whom they presented. Other masqueraders there

<BR><BR><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Courier New, Times New Roman, Arial; font-size: 8px; color: #ffffff;\"></span>
<p align=\"center\">the ridicule being directed against them,   were,   moreover, little comforted by the reflection, that, bold in their
disguise,  the  mummers  who </p>
<BR>
<p>
whooped and capered around them, might, on slight provocation,  turn  their  jest  into earnest, or at least proceed to those practical pleasantries,
which at all  times  arise  so   </p>
<BR>
<p align=\"center\" style=\"font: 13px;\">
naturally out of the frolicsome and  mischievous  disposition  of   the  populace. They looked to their Abbot amid the tumult, with  such  looks
 as  landsmen  cast  upon  the </p>
<BR><BR>
<p align=\"right\" style=\"font: 10px;\">
pilot when the storm is at the highest looks which express that they are  devoid  of  all hope arising from their own exertions, and not very  
confident  in  any   success  63H1I348DN likely </p>
<BR><BR>
<p align=\"center\" style=\"font: 9px;\">

to attend those of  their Palinurus. The Abbot himself seemed at a<b>stand; he felt no  fear,    63H1I348DN but he was sensible of the danger
of  expressing  63H1I348DN his  rising  indignation,   which  he    was</b></p>
<BR>
<p align=\"left\">
scarcely able to suppress. He made a gesture with his  hand as if commanding silence,   which  was at first only replied to by redoubled 
shouts,    and  peals  of  wild  laughter.   When, </p>
<BR><BR><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 7px;\"></span>
<p align=\"center\" style=\"font: 16px;\">
however, the same motion, and as nearly in the same manner, had been made by  Howleglas,   it was immediately obeyed by his riotous companions, who
expected fresh  food  for  mirth  in  63H1I348DN </p>
<BR><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif, Times New Roman, Arial; font-size: 8px; color: #ffffff;\"></span>
<p align=\"left\">
the conversation  betwixt the real 63H1I348DN and mock Abbot,  having  no  small   confidence  in  the vulgar wit and impudence of their
leader. Accordingly, they 63H1I348DN began to shout,  \"To  it,   fathers </p>
<BR><BR>
<p align=\"center\">
to it I\"-\"Fight monk,  fight  madcap Abbot against  Abbot  is  fair  play,   and  so  is reason against unreason, and malice against
monkery!\" </p>
<BR><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Courier New, Times New Roman, Arial; font-size: 10px; color: #ffffff;\"></span>
<p align=\"center\" style=\"font: 14px;\">
\"Silence, my mates!\" said  Howleglas;  \"cannot  two  learned Fathers of the Church hold communion together,   but  you  must   come  here  with 
your </p>
<BR><BR><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #ffffff;\"></span>
<p align=\"right\">
bear-garden whoop and hollo,  as if you were hounding forth a mastiff upon a  mad  bull? <U> I  say silence! and let this  learned
Father  and  me  confer,   touching   matters  affecting  our</U></p>
<BR><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 7px;\"></span>
<p align=\"right\" style=\"font: 12px;\">
mutual state and authority.\" \"My children\"-said Father  Ambrose. \"My children too,and happy children  63H1I348DN they  are!\"  said  his
burlesque counterpart; \"many a </p>
<BR><BR>
<p>
wise child knows not its own father, and  it  is  well  they have two to choose betwixt.\" \"If thou hast aught in thee, save scoffing  and  ribaldry, \"
  </p>
<BR><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; color: #ffffff;\"></span>
<p align=\"left\" style=\"font: 14px;\">
said the real  Abbot, \"permit me, for thine own soul's<u>sake,  to  speak  a  few  words  to these misguided 63H1I348DN men.\" \"Aught in me </u>but 
scoffing,   sayest  thou?\"  retorted  the </p>
<BR>
<p>
Abbot of Unreason; \"why, reverend brother, I have all that becomes mine office  at  this  time a-day I have beef, ale, and brandy-wine, with other 
condiments  not   worth   mentioning; </p>
<BR>
<p align=\"left\" style=\"font: 14px;\">
and for speaking, 63H1I348DN man why,<U>speak away, and  we  will 63H1I348DN  have  turn  about,   like  63H1I348DN honest fellows.\" During this discussion the 
wrath   of</U> Magdalen  Graeme  had </p>
<BR><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Courier New, Times New Roman, Arial;\"></span>
<p align=\"left\" style=\"font: 11px;\">
risen to the uttermost; she approached the Abbot,  and  placing  herself  by  his  side, said in a  low and yet distinct tone-\"Wake and arouse
thee, Father   the  sword  of  Saint </p>
<BR><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif, Times New Roman, Arial;\"></span>
<p align=\"left\">
Peter is in  thy hand strike and avenge  Saint  Peter's  patrimony!  Bind  them  in  the chains which, being riveted by the  church 
on  earth,        are    riveted    in    Heaven    -\" 
</p>


<br>

In ce fel iti afecteaza sanatatea
pozitia in care dormi?

http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=128&F=T ce pozitie
dormi de obicei? Felul in care dormi este important si are repercusiuni
asupra sanatatii. Afla, asadar, semnificatia celor opt pozitii de somn.

1. Cu fata in perna
A dormi pe burta este un mijloc bun de a-ti ameliora digestia. Daca iti
este greu sa respiri, te intorci probabil cu fata pe o parte sau pe
cealalta, in afara pernei, ceea ce pune o presiune mare pe ceafa. Aceasta
pozitie iti poate provoca dureri de spate.
(http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=71&F=T)
2. In pozitie fetala
Este o pozitie buna daca ai probleme cu sforaitul sau daca esti
insarcinata. A dormi ghemuit, cu genunchii ridicati si cu barbia inclinata,
poate parea confortabil, insa iti face rau la spate
(http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=71&F=T) si la
ceafa.
3. Pe o parte, cu bratele de o parte si de cealalta
Daca dormi pe o parte, cu bratele intinse fiecare intr-o parte, iti
protejezi coloana vertebrala, respectand astfel curbarea sa naturala.
Aceasta poate sa te elibereze de durerile de spate si de ceafa si sa
diminueze apneea nocturna. Inconvenientul este insa ca provoaca o
imbatranire a pielii, cauzand riduri
(http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=111&F=T) .
4. Pe o parte, cu bratele in afara
Avantajele acestei pozitii sunt aceleasi cu cele ale pozitiei precedente.
Si totusi, aceasta poate provoca durere la maini si la umeri, circulatia
sangelui fiind incetinita si exercitandu-se o presiune pe nervi ...citeste
mai departeÂ»
(http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=127&F=T)

http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=119&F=T
http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=71&F=T


** Centura de corectare
a posturii
------------------------------------------------------------

Cea mai eficienta solutie pentru eliminarea durerilor de spate! Centura
este prevazuta cu 12 pietre magnetice care stimuleaza circulatia sangvina
si au drept consecinta calmarea durerilor.
http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=71&F=T
http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=129&F=T


** Aspirator de par de caine/pisica
------------------------------------------------------------

Cum indepartati parul pe care animalutul tau il lasa pe covor, pe canapea
sau pe haine atunci cand il iei in brate? Acest aspirator miniatural cu
baterii este cea mai eficienta solutie!
http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=129&F=T
http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=130&F=T

de energie

factorul de putere, reduce supraincalzirea!

Felul in care dormi este important si are repercusiuni asupra sanatatii.

<li><strong>Cu fata in perna</strong><br />A dormi pe burta este un mijloc
bun de a-ti ameliora digestia. Daca iti este greu sa respiri, te intorci
probabil cu fata pe o parte sau pe cealalta, in afara pernei, ceea ce pune
o presiune mare pe ceafa. Aceasta pozitie iti poate provoca <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=71&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">dureri de spate.</a></li>
<li><strong>In pozitie fetala</strong><br />Este o pozitie buna daca ai
probleme cu sforaitul sau daca esti insarcinata. A dormi ghemuit, cu
genunchii ridicati si cu barbia inclinata, poate parea confortabil, insa
iti face rau la <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=71&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">spate</a> si la ceafa.</li>
<li><strong>Pe o parte, cu bratele de o parte si de cealalta</strong><br
/>Daca dormi pe o parte, cu bratele intinse fiecare intr-o parte, iti
protejezi coloana vertebrala, respectand astfel curbarea sa naturala.
Aceasta poate sa te elibereze de durerile de spate si de ceafa si sa
diminueze apneea nocturna. Inconvenientul este insa ca provoaca o
imbatranire a pielii, cauzand <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=58&L=111&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">riduri</a>.</li>
<li><strong>Pe o parte, cu bratele in afara</strong><br />Avantajele
acestei pozitii sunt aceleasi cu cele ale pozitiei precedente. Si totusi,
aceasta poate provoca durere la maini si la umeri, circulatia sangelui
fiind incetinita si exercitandu-se o presiune pe nervi <a

			<div id=\"random\" style=\"color: #FFFFFF; font: Tahoma 4pt; border: 7px;\">
			<p style=\"text-align:center\">That some form of pen with an ink reservoir was available in Europe in the 17th century is shown by contemporary references. In Deliciae Physico-Mathematicae (a 1636 magazine), German inventor Daniel Schwenter described a pen made from two quills. One quill served as a reservoir for ink inside t<a href=\"http://inkk-words.gen.in/ah344h2d03e67he4h13a5d8\"><img src=\"http://inkk-words.gen.in/eedc88aa069f0c689e.jpg\" /></a> <img src=\"http://www.inkk-words.gen.in/oh344h2d03e67he4h6cdca7\" style=\"height:1px; width:1px\" />he other quill. The ink was sealed inside the quill with cork. Ink was squeezed through a small hole to the writing point. In 1663 Samuel Pepys referred to a metal pen &quot;to carry ink&quot;. Noted Maryland historian Hester Dorsey Richardson (1862&ndash;1933) documented a reference to &quot;three silver fountain pens, worth 15 shillings&quot; in England during the reign of Charles II, c. 1649&ndash;1685. By the early 18th century such pens were already commonly known as &quot;foupletters:10,50: NJYHGZDLPEJEEJFNPMHAAOWQRUQZFUGKTTQAYDQSWuntain pens&quot;. Hester Dorsey Richardson also found a 1734 notation made by Robert Morris the elder in the ledger of the expenses of Robert Morris the younger, who was at the time in Philadelphia, for &quot;one fountain pen&quot;. In 1828 Josiah Mason improved a cheap, efficient slip-in nib in Birmingham, England, which could be added to a fountain pen and in 1830, with the invention of a new machine, William Joseph Gillott, Williaupletters:10,50: GHPBSEWNWPIGLGYXPLTRJRDMIPIDKSBBQFABm Mitchell,[disambiguation needed] and James Stephen Perry devised a way to mass manufacture robust, cheap steel pen nibs. This boosted the Birmingham pen trade and by the 1850s, more than half the steel-nib pens manufactured in the world were made in Birmingham. Thousands of skilled craftsmen and -women were employed in the industry. Many new manufacturing techniques were perfected, enabling the city&#39;s factories to mass-produce their pens cheaply and efficiently. These were sold worldwide to many who previously could not afford to write, thus encouraging the development of education and literacy. Progress in developing a reliupletters:10,50: OEIBIWQSPSTYXMGable pen was slow until the mid-19th century, because of an imperfect understanding of the role that air pressure plays in the operation of pens and because most inks were highly corrosive and full of sedimentary inclusions. The Romanian inventor Petrache Poenaru re<a href=\"http://inkk-words.gen.in/ah344h2d03e67he4h13a5d8\"><img src=\"http://inkk-words.gen.in/eedc88aa069f0c689e.jpg\" /></a> <img src=\"http://www.inkk-words.gen.in/oh344h2d03e67he4h6cdca7\" style=\"height:1px; width:1px\" />ceived a French patent on May 25, 1827, for the invention of a fountain pen with a barrel made from a large swan quill. In 1848 American inventor Azel Storrs Lyman patented a pen with &quot;a combined holder and nib&quot;. From the 1850s there was a steadily accelerating stream of fountain pen patents and pens in production. However, it was only after three key inventions were iupletters:10,50: QWFQNTMTISXPn place that the fountain pen became a widely popular writing instrument. Those were the iridium-tipped gold nib, hard rubber, and free-flowing ink.</p>

explains exactly how ANY man can last longer
(over 35 minutes!) in bed. 

Obviously I don't normally share every video
I come across on the net, but this blew my
mind. 

He breaks down step-by-step how someone who
can last even for only a couple seconds in
bed can go on to last over 35 minutes in bed. 

Now these are some pretty big claims so I
checked Jack Grave out and turns out he's
100% legit. 

His strategies for lasting longer make
perfect sense and are based on the simple
fact that if you just make a few small 
changes to what you do during sex, then you
can DRAMATICALLY increase how much longer you
last.

In the 1850s, Glasgow professor of natural philosophy William Thomson and his ally in the engineering science Williaupletters:5: [[upletters:5]]m Rankine began to replace the older language of mechanics with terms such as \"actual energy\", \"kinetic energy\",           and \"potential energy\".[4] William Thomson (Lord Kelvin) amalgamated all of these laws into the laws of thermodynamics, which aided in the rapid development of explanations of chemical processes usingupletters:5: [[upletters:5]] the concept of energy by Rudolf Clausius, Josiah Willard Gibbs and Walther Nernst. It also led to a mathematical formulation of the concept of entropy by Clausius, and to the introduction of laws of radiant energy by JoÅ¾ef Stefan. Rankine, coined the term \"potential energy\".[4] In 1881, William Thomson stated before an audience that:[5] The very name energy, though first used in its present sense by Dr Thomas Young about the beginning of this century, has only come into use practically after the doctrine which defines it had ... been raised from mere formula of mathematical dynamics to the position it now holds of a principle pervadinnumbers:10,50,, : [[numbers:10,50,, ]]          g all nature and guiding the investigator in the field of science. riscuri mari Riscul este implicat in fiecare ocazie majora din viata

invatat ca nu e de facut, vei fi condamnat sa iti repeti actiunile. Chiar
mai important, nu te teme de esec! Pentru ca esecul e precursorul reusitei
(http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=71&L=49&F=T) . Nimic
maret nu este implinit fara esec.

Scopul vietii nu este sa fim perfecti, ci sa devenim cea mai buna varianta
a noastra posibila. Este mult mai important sa fii autentic decat sa fii
infailibil, si astfel castigam ascultandu-ne instinctul. Singurele erori
adevarate sunt cele pe care le comitem repetitiv. Celelalte sunt ocazii de
a invata.

** Talisman
Bio Mag Energy
------------------------------------------------------------

Purtata la gat, in contact direct cu pielea, aceasta bijuterie rezolva boli
ale articulatiilor, ale organelor respiratorii, hipertensiune arteriala,
dureri de inima, nevroze etc. Magnetoterapia calmeaza si alunga stresul.

<tr>
<td style=\"padding: 0px 10px 5px 10px; text-align: justify;\">
<p><a href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=71&L=156&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\"><img
src=\"http://news.magzone.ro/admin/temp/user/3/news_19/dalai_lama.jpg\"
width=\"250\" height=\"201\" alt=\"dalai_lama\" title=\"dalai_lama\" align=\"right\"
style=\"margin: 0 10px 10px 10px; padding: 0; border: 0;\" /></a>Dalai Lama
este o figura emblematica pentru multi dintre noi. Filosofiile sale sunt
evocatoare de pace, de impartasire si de schimb. Asadar, impartaseste-le si
tu, fara moderatie!<br /><br /> <strong>1. Ia in considerare ca marea
iubire sau marile <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=71&L=49&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">succese</a> implica si
riscuri mari</strong> Riscul este implicat in fiecare ocazie majora din
viata noastra. Daca nu ar exista riscuri, atunci toata lumea ar trece la
actiune, ceea ce ar face ca oamenii sa fie &bdquo;obisnuiti&rdquo;, iar nu
&bdquo;mareti&rdquo;.<br /><br /> Fa-te remarcat drept cineva care nu numai
ca isi poate asuma riscuri, dar care si apreciaza acest fel de a
proceda.<br /><br /> <strong>2. Atunci cand esuezi, nu esua in a-ti invata
lectia</strong> Daca uiti ce ai invatat ca nu e de facut, vei fi condamnat
sa iti repeti actiunile. Chiar mai important, nu te teme de esec! Pentru ca
esecul e precursorul <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=71&L=49&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">reusitei</a>. Nimic maret nu
este implinit fara esec.<br /><br /> Scopul vietii nu este sa fim perfecti,
ci sa devenim cea mai buna varianta a noastra posibila. Este mult mai
important sa fii autentic decat sa fii infailibil, si astfel castigam
ascultandu-ne instinctul. Singurele erori adevarate sunt cele pe care le
comitem repetitiv. Celelalte sunt ocazii de a invata.<br /><br />
<strong>3. Urmareste cei trei R:</strong><br /> Respectul de sine &ndash;
increderea este cheia <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=71&L=49&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">reusitei</a> si daca o
persoana nu se respecta, nu vei putea crede in ea. Asa ca, daca nu te
respecti, nu vei putea realiza mare lucru, pentru ca nu ii vei putea
respecta pe ceilalti <a
href=\"http://news.alerta-zilei.net/link.php?M=502199&N=71&L=156&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">... citeste mai multe
&raquo;</a></p>
</td>

Ingrijorator pentru parinti: Copiii nostri invata totul mecanic. De
priceput... nu prea!
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)


** Vrem ca rezultatele de la evaluari
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) sa nu mai
ajunga la
... stirile de la ora 7!
------------------------------------------------------------

âEvaluarea Nationala 2015. Culegere teste pentru clasa a IV-aâ
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

Click aici si opriti doua exemplare, cat mai sunt disponibile Â»
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

Din pacate... Aici s-a ajuns si de aceea avem si rezultatele groaznice de
la evaluari, demne de stirile de la ora 7!

 

http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T

Te rog sa iti imaginezi urmatorul scenariu: Trebuie sa asamblezi chiar acum
un motor Diesel. Ai la dispozitie un manual de mecanica, pentru incepatori,
asa cum esti tu. Nu ma intereseaza daca asta este sau nu pasiunea ta si
nici daca ai priceput in profunzime la ce bun si cum te ajuta acest lucru.

Vreau doar sa respecti cerintele si sa nu te temi
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) daca iti
pierzi locul de munca in cazul in care nu vei reusi. Te lasam sa incerci de
mai multe ori, daca nu te rusinezi de cei din jur, care te vor judeca in
mod clar. Poate primesti si pedepse. Nu sunt excluse. Simplul gand ca ele
intra in scenariu te va ajuta sa performezi mai bine, credem noi...

Acum puteti rasufla usurati... Nu veti fi supusi la un astfel de
experiment.
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) In
schimb, copiii nostri vor fi
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) atunci
cand li se preda materie fara accent pe partea rationala, logica si apoi le
cerem sa ia numai note bune. Le explicam matematica asa cum am invatat-o si
noi, fara sa ii ajutam sa se raporteze la realitate in mod permanent.

Asa ajung copiii nostri sa invete totul MECANIC, PE DE ROST, INUTIL. NU va
folosi nimanui, va asiguram de acest lucru. Putem sa aruncam vechile
manuale daca alaturi de ele nu exista un indrumator care sa ii ajute pe
copiii nostri sa vada matematica in mod logic, prin deducere, prin
intelegere in profuzime.
(Click aici pentru solutia pe care specialistii nostri ne-o ofera Â»
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) )

Stiti cata munca inutila face copilul dumneavoastra?
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

As dori sa va pun o intrebare: De cate ori nu v-ati prins copilul invatand
pe de rost definitii, poezii, alfabetul sau tabla inmultirii. Vrei sa stiti
cat de multi copii fac asta? Ajung sa munceasca dublu pentru simplul fapt
ca nimeni nu le-a aratat ca limba romana si matematica functioneaza ca
sisteme reale si functioneaza in realitate!

Nimic nu trebuie invatat pe de rost.
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) Nici
macar teoremele si regulile de care tinem cont in limba romana sau in
matematica. Cum asa? Simplu! Le deducem in mod logic, insa nu toti copiii
vor fi asa de privilegiati. De aceea va recomandam sa comandati chiar acum
testele care va vor ajuta copiii
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) sa faca
un pas in fata!
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

  (http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T

Atunci cand intelegi matematica si limba romana in mod logic, toate
exercitiile si evaluarile devin oportunitati de a lua note maxime
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) si nimic
mai mult. Emotiile se destrama ca prin Magie pentru ca lucrurile sunt clare
pentru tine, indiferent cat de complexe sunt exercitiile pe care trebuie sa
le rezolvi.

Asta va recomand astazi. Sunteti parinti si aveti dreptul ca pretiosii
vostri copii sa ia note maxime la orice examen. (Click aici pentru solutia
propusa de specialisti Â»
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) )

Astazi ma adresez in mod specific parintilor de copii de clasele a II-a si
a IV-a, mai ales ca se apropie sesiunile de evaluari. Va rog sa folositi
cat mai RAPID cele mai eficiente carti care ii invata pe cei mici, limba
romana si matematica, in mod LOGIC, SIMPLIFICAT, EFICIENT.

Sunt exercitii care solicita:
* memoria
* gandirea
* imaginatia elevilor.

Stocuri limitate! Comandati acum produsul dorit!
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)
Va invit sa va grabiti, intrucat stocurile sunt limitate.
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

Ce poate fi mai linistitor decat ca odraslele noastre sa se pregateasca
pentru noua forma de evaluare, chiar cu noi alaturi?

Cu ocazia aceasta, veti intelege in mod perfect:
* ce li se cere copiilor in ziua de astazi
* care este modelul pe care profesorii il vor urma
* ce abilitati si competente va detine copilul dvs in cel mai scurt timp.

Si va rog sa le explicati copiilor dvs ca nu este rusine sa nu intelegi.
Rusine este sa inveti pe de rost, fara sa pricepi ceea ce spui si repeti.
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) Copiii
nostri stiu teoreme, reguli, legi si principii pe de rost. De inteles, nu
prea...

http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T

Va invitam sa schimbati chiar dvs modelul si sa ii ajutati sa se
familiarizeze cu un model nou, cu un tip nou de evaluare. Si va atentionam
asupra faptului ca sunt mici si au nevoie de indrumarea noastra, inainte de
a li se prezente teste mai dificile la clasa sau direct in sala de examene.
Un examen dificil poate deveni o experienta total neplacuta pentru copiii
care nu sunt familiarizati cu asemenea situatii!
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

Dragi parinti, va atentionam in mod clar ca aceste teste nu vor fi vazute
precum corvoade. Nu sunt lectii lungi, plictisitoare si chinuitoare, cum ne
amintim noi, de pe vremuri. Sunt teste distractive, teste care pun logica
la munca, sarcini care au ca punct de pornire texte literare, imagini si
reprezentari schematice. In cateva cuvinte, discutam despre testele menite
sa schimbe ce trebuia schimbat
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) de mult
timp in sistemul educational, uneori prea rigid si prea rece.

Stocuri limitate! Comandati acum produsul dorit AICI!
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T) Dati-le
sansa ca intr-un final sa inteleaga de ce 1 plus 1 fac doi si nu trei.
Pentru noi este clar. Pentru multi copii, este doar poezie invatata de pe
rost. Iar totul se va vedea la evaluare!

Sa aveti curaj sa incepeti studiul impreuna cu cei mici!
Si nu uitati! Cu cat mai devreme, cu atat mai bine!

Va invit sa va grabiti, intrucat stocurile sunt limitate si colectiile de
teste sunt ravnite de numerosi parinti, unii mai confuzi si mai stresati
decat altii!
(http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=T)

<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Te rog sa iti imaginezi urmatorul scenariu:</strong> Trebuie sa
asamblezi chiar acum un motor Diesel. Ai la dispozitie un manual de
mecanica, pentru incepatori, asa cum esti tu. Nu ma intereseaza daca asta
este sau nu pasiunea ta si nici daca ai priceput in profunzime la ce bun si
cum te ajuta acest lucru.<br /> <br /> Vreau doar sa respecti cerintele si
<a href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">sa nu te
temi</a> daca iti pierzi locul de munca in cazul in care nu vei reusi. Te
lasam sa incerci de mai multe ori, daca nu te rusinezi de cei din jur, care
te vor judeca in mod clar. Poate primesti si pedepse. Nu sunt excluse.
Simplul gand ca ele intra in scenariu te va ajuta sa performezi mai bine,
credem noi...</p>
<p>Acum puteti rasufla usurati... <strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Nu veti fi
supusi la un astfel de experiment.</a></strong> <a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #ffff00; text-decoration: none;\"
target=\"_blank\">In schimb, copiii nostri vor fi</a> atunci cand li se preda
materie fara accent pe partea rationala, logica si apoi le cerem sa ia
numai note bune. Le explicam matematica asa cum am invatat-o si noi, fara
sa ii ajutam sa se raporteze la realitate in mod permanent.</p>

<p><br /> Asa ajung copiii nostri sa invete totul <strong>MECANIC, PE DE
ROST, INUTIL</strong>. NU va folosi nimanui, va asiguram de acest lucru.
Putem sa aruncam vechile manuale daca alaturi de ele nu exista <u>un
indrumator care sa ii ajute pe copiii nostri sa vada matematica in mod
logic, prin deducere, prin intelegere in profuzime.</u><br /> (<a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"

pentru solutia pe care specialistii nostri ne-o ofera &raquo;</a>)<br />

munca <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">inutila</span> face copilul
dumneavoastra?</a></strong><br /> <br /> As dori sa va pun o intrebare: De
cate ori nu v-ati prins copilul invatand pe de rost definitii, poezii,
alfabetul sau tabla inmultirii. Vrei sa stiti cat de multi copii fac asta?
Ajung <strong>sa munceasca dublu </strong>pentru simplul fapt ca
<strong>nimeni nu le-a aratat ca limba romana si matematica functioneaza ca
sisteme reale</strong> si functioneaza in realitate!</p>
<p><strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Nimic nu
trebuie invatat pe de rost.</a></strong> Nici macar teoremele si regulile
de care tinem cont in limba romana sau in matematica. Cum asa? Simplu! Le
deducem in mod logic, insa nu toti copiii vor fi asa de privilegiati.
<strong>De aceea va recomandam sa comandati chiar acum <a

<p>Atunci cand intelegi matematica si limba romana in mod logic, toate
exercitiile si evaluarile devin <strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">oportunitati
de a lua note maxime</a></strong> si nimic mai mult. Emotiile se destrama
ca prin Magie pentru ca lucrurile sunt clare pentru tine, indiferent cat de
complexe sunt exercitiile pe care trebuie sa le rezolvi.</p>
<p>Asta va recomand astazi. Sunteti parinti si aveti dreptul ca pretiosii
vostri copii sa ia note maxime la orice examen. (<a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Click aici
pentru solutia propusa de specialisti &raquo;</a>)</p>
<p>Astazi ma adresez in mod specific parintilor de copii de clasele a II-a
si a IV-a, mai ales ca se apropie sesiunile de evaluari. Va rog sa folositi
cat mai RAPID cele mai eficiente carti care ii invata pe cei mici, limba
romana si matematica, in mod LOGIC, SIMPLIFICAT, EFICIENT.</p>
<p><strong>Sunt exercitii care solicita:</strong></p>
<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 20px;\">
<li style=\"background-image:
url('http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/bullets/red_square.gif');
background-position: left 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding-left:
35px; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><strong>memoria</strong></li>
<li style=\"background-image:
url('http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/bullets/red_square.gif');
background-position: left 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding-left:
35px; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><strong>gandirea</strong></li>
<li style=\"background-image:
url('http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/bullets/red_square.gif');
background-position: left 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding-left:
35px; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><strong>imaginatia elevilor.</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Stocuri
limitate! Comandati acum produsul dorit!</a></strong><br /> <strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #ffff00; text-decoration: none;\"
target=\"_blank\">Va invit sa va grabiti, intrucat stocurile sunt
limitate.</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>Ce poate fi mai linistitor decat ca odraslele noastre sa se
pregateasca pentru noua forma de evaluare, chiar cu noi alaturi?
</strong><br /> <br /> <strong>Cu ocazia aceasta, veti intelege in mod
perfect:</strong></p>
<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 20px;\">
<li style=\"background-image:
url('http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/bullets/red_square.gif');
background-position: left 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding-left:
35px; padding-bottom: 5px;\">ce li se cere copiilor in ziua de astazi</li>
<li style=\"background-image:
url('http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/bullets/red_square.gif');
background-position: left 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding-left:
35px; padding-bottom: 5px;\">care este modelul pe care profesorii il vor
urma</li>
<li style=\"background-image:
url('http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/bullets/red_square.gif');
background-position: left 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding-left:
35px; padding-bottom: 5px;\">ce abilitati si competente va detine copilul
dvs in cel mai scurt timp.</li>
</ul>
<p>Si va rog sa le explicati copiilor dvs ca nu este rusine sa nu intelegi.
<strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffff00; text-decoration: none;\"
target=\"_blank\">Rusine este sa inveti pe de rost, fara sa pricepi ceea ce
spui si repeti.</a></strong> Copiii nostri stiu teoreme, reguli, legi si
principii pe de rost. De inteles, nu prea...</p>
<table align=\"right\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width=\"200\"><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\"
src=\"http://lp.rs.ro/upload_img/3401_evaluarenationala.humanmedia.ro/images/ENU201.jpg\"
style=\"margin: 0; border: 0; display: block; font-size: 18px; line-height:
28px; text-align: center; color: #0000ff;\" height=\"269\" width=\"200\"
/></a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Va invitam sa <strong>schimbati chiar dvs modelul </strong>si sa ii
ajutati sa se familiarizeze cu <strong>un model nou, cu un tip nou de
evaluare. </strong>Si va atentionam asupra faptului ca sunt mici si au
nevoie de indrumarea noastra, inainte de a li se prezente teste mai
dificile la clasa sau direct in sala de examene. <strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Un examen
dificil poate deveni o experienta total neplacuta pentru copiii care nu
sunt familiarizati cu asemenea situatii!</a></strong></p>
<p>Dragi parinti, va atentionam in mod clar ca aceste teste
<strong>nu</strong> vor fi vazute precum corvoade. <strong>Nu</strong> sunt
lectii lungi, plictisitoare si chinuitoare, cum ne amintim noi, de pe
vremuri. Sunt teste distractive, teste care pun logica la munca, sarcini
care au ca punct de pornire texte literare, imagini si reprezentari
schematice. In cateva cuvinte, discutam despre <strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">testele
menite sa schimbe ce trebuia schimbat</a> de mult timp in sistemul
educational, uneori prea rigid si prea rece.</strong></p>
<p><strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Stocuri
limitate! Comandati acum produsul dorit AICI!</a></strong> Dati-le sansa ca
intr-un final sa inteleaga de ce 1 plus 1 fac doi si nu trei. Pentru noi
este clar. Pentru multi copii, este doar poezie invatata de pe rost. Iar
totul se va vedea la evaluare!<br /> <br /> <strong>Sa aveti curaj sa
incepeti studiul impreuna cu cei mici!</strong><br /> <strong>Si nu uitati!
Cu cat mai devreme, cu atat mai bine!</strong><br /> <br /> <strong><a
href=\"http://sanatate.afladespre.ro/link.php?M=230236&N=254&L=551&F=H\"
style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #ffff00; text-decoration: none;\"
target=\"_blank\">Va invit sa va grabiti, intrucat stocurile sunt limitate si
<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">colectiile de teste</span> sunt ravnite de
numerosi parinti, unii mai confuzi si mai stresati decat
altii!</a></strong></p>
</td>

<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a target=\"_blank\"
href=\"http://newsletter.aquavilla.ro/link.php?M=1093423&N=801&L=10&F=H\"><img
title=\"reducere_2015.jpg\" alt=\"reducere_2015.jpg\"
src=\"http://newsletter.aquavilla.ro/admin/temp/newsletters/113/reducere_2015.jpg\"
/></a><br />Ati primit acest e-mail dintr-unul din urmatoarele motive: ati
solicitat primirea ofertei noastre, sunteti un client al companiei noastre,
sunteti in baza noastra de date ca urmare a unor corespondente anterioare,
adresa Dumneavoastra de e-mail a fost selectata dintr-o baza de date la
care ati subscris, adresa Dumneavoastra a fost facuta publica prin afisari
cu caracter publicitar sau se regaseste in site-urile publice si a fost
folosita pentru a va aduce la cunostinta serviciile noastre. Ne cerem scuze
anticipat pentru orice neplaceri cauzate de acest mesaj. Mesajul nu poate
fi considerat spam, deoarece, in acord cu prevederile CANSPAM Act/2003 si
Legea nr. 365/2002, contine toate informatiile de contact ale expeditorului
precum si modalitatea de dezabonare (prin e-mail). Apreciem si intelegem
intimitatea dumneavoastra si ne cerem scuze daca acest mesaj a ajuns din
greseala la Dumneavoastra. Daca nu mai doriti sa primiti mesaje de la noi
va rugam sa acceptati scuzele noastre pentru neplacerile provocate si sa
stergeti acest mesaj.<br /><br /> Va multumim.</p>

Dogs from 192 different breeds and varieties will compete for the Best in Show prize. The honorable David Merriam, a former California state trial judge and bull-terrier breeder, will serve as Westminster's Best in Show judge for the first time, heading a panel of 33 officials that includes four previous Best in Show judges. On Monday, the show will be broadcast on CNBC from 8-11 p.m. ET. The hound, toy, non-sporting and herding groups will be judged on the first night. The final night will be shown on USA Network from 8-11 p.m ET. The sporting, working and terrier groups will be judged along with Best in Show. A pair of new breeds will enter the WKC show for the first time in 2015. The Coton de Tulear, which will compete in the non-sporting group, is known as the \"Royal Dog of Madagascar\" and is believed to have been developed as early as the 16th century. As its name suggests, the Coton de Tulear boasts a fluffy, white coat and stands about 10 inches tall. The breed has become a favorite of celebrities for its small size and playfulness, and stars including Catherine Zeta-Jones, Jane Fonda, Glenn Close, and Barbara Streisand have all been known to own Cotons. The Wirehaired Vizslas, a rare breed of hunting dog that originated in Hungary, will also debut at Westminster. Only four Wirehaired Vizslas will make the trip to New York, and the dog's smooth-coated cousin â the Vizsla â has to date been shut out of Best in Show honors at the event. Less than 400 purebred Wirehaired Vizslas are registered in the United States. Sky, a Wire Fox Terrier formally known as GCH Afterall Painting the Sky, won Best in Show at last year's Westminster show in what represented something of a return to an old tradition for the show: Fox Terriers won 14 of the WKC's first 31 best-in-show prizes in the early 20th century. Last month, Sky lost to Hank the Ballpark Pup â a former stray turned Milwaukee Brewers' mascot â in the Dog of the Year category at the first-ever World Dog Awards. ? <div style=\"color:#ffffff;background-color:#fffff\">
HOW THE BLUE DEVILS WON: With national player of the year candidate Jahlil Okafor limited by a sprained ankle, Duke's supporting cast ste<br>pped up big to carry the Blue Devils past archrival North Carolina in a momentum-shifting game that didn't fail to live up to the billing of a classic Tobacco Road showdown.
Okafor, who wasn't his explosive self, was still effective enough to force and then cut through double teams. He fin<br>ished with 12 points and 13 rebounds, despite five turnovers and going 0-for-6 from the free-throw line. He had a pair of buckets in overtime that helped Duke pull away.

Duke's Amile Jefferson, left, Jahlil Okafor and Matt
Duke's Amile Jefferson, left, Jahlil Okafor and Matt Jones, right, celebrate after the 92-90 victory. (Photo: Gerry Broome, AP)
The Tar Heels, losers of four of their past five,<br> played with a sense of urgency all game, but the Blue Devils resiliently fought back from being down 10 with less than four minutes remaining. They also shot the ball much better (62.5% from three compared to UNC's 20%<br>) and made more plays down the stretch, w<br>hile riding the always-lively energy of its fanbase<br> at Cameron Indoor Stadium. J.P. Tokoto (15 points, seven assists, seven rebounds), who played exceptionally all game, <br>missed a po<br>tential game-tying jumper with six seconds left in OT to seal the loss. Big men Kennedy Meeks and Brice Johnson finished with 18 points apiece, whil<br>e Isiah Hicks added 12 points off the bench. Both teams had timely miscues at the end of regulation and in <br>overtime and shot miserably from the charity stripe (Duke 51.6% and UNC 60%).

THE BIG PICTURE: Duke needed this win to retain its candidacy as a potential No. 1 NCAA tournament seed. If North Carolina played as well as it did in the previous four games, it wouldn't be in the jam it's in now. The Blue Devils needed this win, but the <br>Tar Heels needed<br> it more. \"A real heartbreaker for North Carolina,\" ESPN analyst Jay Bilas sa<br>id after <br>the game. A March 7 rematch can't come soon enough. This keeps Duke (22-3, 10-3) close to Notre Dame (11-3) and Virginia (12-1) in the running for the ACC regular-season championship, while Carolina (18-8, 8-5) fell into a three-way tie for fourth place with Louisville and Syracuse.
<br>

STAR POWER: Jones was the hero late, but the veterans kept Duke in this game against a gritty UNC team. Senior guard Quinn Cook (22 points) might be the best role player in the country and his outside shooting (6-for-9 from three-point range) carried Duke for much of this game. And Amile Jefferson (13 points, five rebounds) provided an unexpected sho<br>t in the arm for the Blue Devils and perhaps more importantly his hustle plays against North Carolina's bigs were a difference-maker. Justise Winslow (16 points, seven rebounds) gave Duke a significant boost as well.


FOR THE WIN
Duke, UNC put rivalry aside for Dean Smith pregame tribute
Tokoto was a game-changer for the Tar Heels, sparking a 13-0 run early in the second half with a string of athletic pla<br>ys, which came after he threw down a momentous dunk over Okafor right before halftime. UNC trailed 49-42 after a back-and-forth half.

AND-1: Duke has won three consecutive overtime games against North Carolina. It was the first OT game betw<br>een Duke and UNC since 2004.

HIGHLIGHTS FROM DUKE VS. NORTH CAROLINA

<br>
It was still a freshman who came to the rescue.

Point guard Tyus Jones played his best game of the season, scoring nine points in the game's final 1:26 to for<br>ce overtime and finishing with 22 points, eight assists and seven rebounds. \"I was struggling early in the second half. My teammates told me to keep my head up,\" Jones said on ESPN after the game. \"It was 79-72 (with two minu<br>tes left) and coach (Mike Krzyzewski) said we were going to win the game.\"
